Ind-Barath Power Said to Sign 26.6 Billion Rupee Loan With Banks

-- B y   A n u r a g   J o s h i
-- 
2011-02-28T05:34:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/ind-barath-power-said-to-sign-26-6-billion-rupee-loan-with-banks.html
Ind-Barath Power Madras Ltd., an
Indian electricity producer, signed 26.6 billion rupees ($588
million) of loans, according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  A phone call made to the company by Bloomberg News for
confirmation was left unanswered.  To contact the reporter on this story:
